                                    Shelter Water Control Zone Statement of Water Quality
                                    Objectives</docTitle><enactingFormula role="empoweringSection">(<ref href="/hk/cap358/s5">Cap.
                                                358, section
                                    5</ref>)<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></enactingFormula><commencementNote>[28 July 1989]</commencementNote><sourceNote>(Format changes—<ref href="hk/2019/er6">E.R. 6 of 2019</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1438403055756_002" name="s" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="s" class="left_indent_0 no_header"><num value="0"></num><content><br></br>The
            water quality objectives set out in the first column of <ref>Schedule 1</ref> have been
            established for those parts of the Port Shelter Water Control Zone defined in
                <ref>Schedule 2</ref> set opposite those water quality objectives in the second
            column of <ref>Schedule 1</ref>.</content></section><schedule id="ID_1438403055772_001" name="sch1" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="sch1"><num value="1">Schedule 1</num><content>
