                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <p>B.</p>
                        </td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <p>BACTERIA</p>
                        </td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <paragraph xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" name="1" temporalId="sch1_1" id="ID_1571369314959_006"><num class="align_right" value="1">(a)</num><content class="align_justified">The level of Escherichia coli
                                    should not exceed 610 per 100 mL, calculated as the geometric
                                    mean of all samples collected in one calendar year.</content></paragraph>
                        </td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td>
                            <p>Secondary Contact Recreation Subzones and Fish Culture Subzones</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <paragraph xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" name="1" temporalId="sch1_1" id="ID_1571369314959_007"><num class="align_right" value="1">(b)</num><content class="align_justified">The level of Escherichia coli
                                    should not exceed 180 per 100 mL, calculated as the geometric
                                    mean of all samples collected from March to October inclusive in
                                    one calendar year. Samples should be taken at least 3 times in a
                                    calendar month at intervals of between 3 and 14 days.</content></paragraph>
                        </td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td>
                            <p>Bathing Beach Subzones</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td colspan="2"></td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <p class="align_right"><sourceNote xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">(<ref href="hk/1991/ln452">L.N. 452 of
                                1991</ref>)</sourceNote></p>
                        </td>
