                        </td>
                        <td colspan="2"></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <p>M.</p>
                        </td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <p>DANGEROUS SUBSTANCES</p>
                        </td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <paragraph xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" name="1" temporalId="sch1_1" id="ID_1571369315052_019"><num class="align_right" value="1">(a)</num><content class="align_justified">Waste discharges shall not cause
                                    the concentration of dangerous substances in the water to attain
                                    such levels as to produce significant toxic effects in humans,
                                    fish or any other aquatic organisms, with due regard to
                                    biologically cumulative effects in food chains and to toxicant
                                    interactions with each other.</content></paragraph>
                        </td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td>
                            <p>Whole Zone</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <paragraph xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" name="1" temporalId="sch1_1" id="ID_1571369315052_020"><num class="align_right" value="1">(b)</num><content class="align_justified">Waste discharges of dangerous
                                    substances shall not put a risk to any designated beneficial
                                    uses of the aquatic environment.</content></paragraph>
                        </td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td>
                            <p>Whole Zone</p>
                        </td>
