                        </td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <p>TURBIDITY</p>
                        </td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <p>No changes in turbidity or other factors arising from waste
                                discharges shall reduce light transmission substantially from the
                                normal level.</p>
                        </td>
